      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1956387454,
      "version": 956,
      "versionNonce": 76201698,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773592329717,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n * Dev Core System Packages (git, openssl, curl/wget, yq/jq, 7z/tar,\nbtop, nmap, tcpdump, vim/nano/emacs, gcc, ...)\n\n * Default dev user \"smith\" @sudoers (configurable)\n\n * Pre-Configured ZSH Shell w/ \"OhMyPosh\" Enhancer by default\n\n * \"MISE\" pre installed as central Env/Tool manager.\n\n * Mise base tools:\n   - sd, ripgrep, fzf, zoxide\n   - zellij, yazi\n   - helix/neovim\n   - opencode\n\n * Enklum Cli (Show Dnf+Mise pgks, trigger updates)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "zJ82pdEktUsv_aJSnaJwk",
      "originalText": "\n * Dev Core System Packages (git, openssl, curl/wget, yq/jq, 7z/tar, btop, nmap, tcpdump, vim/nano/emacs, gcc, ...)\n\n * Default dev user \"smith\" @sudoers (configurable)\n\n * Pre-Configured ZSH Shell w/ \"OhMyPosh\" Enhancer by default\n\n * \"MISE\" pre installed as central Env/Tool manager.\n\n * Mise base tools:\n   - sd, ripgrep, fzf, zoxide\n   - zellij, yazi\n   - helix/neovim\n   - opencode\n\n * Enklum Cli (Show Dnf+Mise pgks, trigger updates)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
